{"tid":1697484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智利總統稱以應對暴徒同樣力度 起訴濫權警察","createTime":"2019-11-07T01:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T01:46:26.000Z","uid":186071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"52f470825f033916b4fbf4eeed75685ef0a1f5f8","tid":1697484,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"智利民眾抗議地鐵加價引發的示威持續，至今造成超過20人死亡，7000多人被捕。檢察官說，正調查800多宗有關警方使用過份武力及強姦示威者的指控，並會尋求法院授權拘留涉嫌虐待示威者的14名警員。<br />\n總統皮涅拉承諾，會以應對暴徒同樣的力度，起訴濫權的警察及士兵，強調任何時候及任何情況下，都完全尊重人權，他早前宣布進入緊急狀態時，已經要求武裝部隊遵守國際使用武力的規定。<br />\n正擔任聯合國人權事務高級專員的智利前總統巴切萊特，亦派出小組到智利，與懷疑受害人會面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/智利總統稱以應對暴徒同樣力度-起訴濫權警察-232950623.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%A8%B1%E4%BB%A5%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E5%90%8C%E6%A8%A3%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6-%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E6%BF%AB%E6%AC%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-232950623.html&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=19ef2e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/智利總統稱以應對暴徒同樣力度-起訴濫權警察-232950623.html</a>"},{"pid":"f6e16afe7e975393cae78fd212ced6a009a941f5","tid":1697484,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"人地仆街極都會做下樣起訴班警賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n西方果然係西方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9923c83f159c15b442a2e6c87f11349da6bc2f","tid":1697484,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6e16afe7e975393cae78fd212ced6a009a941f5","tid":1697484,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"人地仆街極都會做下樣起訴班警賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n西方果然係西方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:40:41.000Z","msg":"佢要對人民負責<br />\n林鄭對中央負責"